{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"OrangeCompactTheme","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeCompactTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeCompactTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange Compact"}],"externalID":"s:23OUDSThemesOrangeCompact0bC5ThemeC"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/OrangeCompactTheme\/init(fontFamily:tuning:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Orange Compact"},{"text":" theme is an Orange theme but tailored for some products with heavy UI.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeCompactTheme","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Usages","anchor":"Usages","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some products may have heavy and very rich user interfaces with a lot of components and elements to displays and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with which users can interact. Thus for such products there are specific constraints of spaces and sizes, even if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these products must be Orange flavored."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"That is the reason why this team is created: a kind of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" but wih adjustments on some tokens like spacings and sizings."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To get the theme:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Integration","level":2,"text":"Integration","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To use this theme, inject it to your view using ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and get it through environment variable.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @main","    struct YourApp: App {","        var body: some Scene {","            WindowGroup {","                OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeCompactTheme()) {","                    \/\/ Your root view","                }","            }","        }","    }"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Theme tuning","anchor":"Theme-tuning","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The theme can be customized a bit for more flexibility thanks to "},{"code":"Tuning","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You just need to give a predefined tuning configuration at theme init to build the one you need."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To apply the tuning:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your theme tuning","    let tuning = Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true, hasRoundedAlertMessages: false)","","    \/\/ Apply it to your theme","    let theme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: tuning)","    \/\/ Or in one line","    let theme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true, hasRoundedAlertMessages: false))","","    \/\/ Or apply predefined tunings","    let orangeFranceTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeFrance)","    let orangeBusinessTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeBusiness)","    let maxitTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: Tuning.MaxIt)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Typography","anchor":"Typography","type":"heading","level":2},{"text":"Helvetica Neue","anchor":"Helvetica-Neue","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange brand strongly relies on the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" font family. Thus each Orange brand should, or must, use it."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For iOS the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" font family is available at system level, so it is not needed to get it through external assets."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"By default an instance of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeCompactTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" uses as font family the token "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault"},{"type":"text","text":", which is today "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use another font family, you will have to send the suitable token or the suitable font family."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, beware, iOS API relies also on the PostScript name of the font."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To be sure of the value to use, look at the font book of your device."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is recommended to use the font raw tokens."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ The following instanciations work","    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme()","    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(fontFamily: OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault)","    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(fontFamily: \"HelveticaNeue\") \/\/ Which is PostScript name of the font","    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(fontFamily: \"Helvetica Neue\")"]},{"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue-Arabic","level":3,"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family does not manage arabic alphabet but latin one, it is possible apply another font family to the theme like the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":". This font family assets can be retrieved through the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"PostScript name management has been implemented for this font family, thus the weight are managed and it is only needed to add the font assets to the project,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"register them and define the font family name to use."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(fontFamily: \"Helvetica Neue Arabic\")"]},{"anchor":"Tokens-versions","level":2,"text":"Tokens versions","type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Core OUDS version: 1.9.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Core Orange version: 1.2.0","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Brand Orange Compact version: 2.3.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.17.0","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangecompact\/orangecompacttheme"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/OrangeCompactTheme","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Inherits From","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"],"type":"inheritsFrom","kind":"relationships"},{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/SQ","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/OUDSTheme":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/oudstheme","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","abstract":[{"text":"This is a basic theme any theme must be a subclass off, or all themes must have as ancestor.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A Swift ","type":"text"},{"code":"class","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been used so as to allow to easily override some attributes and have inheritance, without having for developers","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to implement all tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"object oriented paradigm"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"theme contract","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is not a "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"final","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" class, its type cannot be seen as "},{"code":"Sendable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", that is the reason why this conformity is unchecked."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTheme"}],"title":"OUDSTheme"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/s8SendableP":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/s8SendableP","title":"Swift.Sendable","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/OrangeCompactTheme/init(fontFamily:tuning:)":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"fontFamily","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FontFamilySemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic010FontFamilyB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tuning","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Tuning","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract6Tuninga","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Constructor of the OrangeCompact theme with its own providers of tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It uses also the providers of charts colors from Orange theme (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeColorChartSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangecompact\/orangecompacttheme\/init(fontfamily:tuning:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/OrangeCompactTheme\/init(fontFamily:tuning:)","title":"init(fontFamily:tuning:)","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact":{"title":"Theme Orange Compact","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange Compact theme is dedicated to applications with strong dimensions constraints."}],"role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangecompact","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orangecompact.png"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact"},"ic_theme_orangecompact.png":{"identifier":"ic_theme_orangecompact.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/ic_theme_orangecompact.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/OrangeCompactTheme":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeCompactTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Orange Compact"},{"text":" theme is an Orange theme but tailored for some products with heavy UI.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangecompact\/orangecompacttheme","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/OrangeCompactTheme","title":"OrangeCompactTheme","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeCompactTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/SQ":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/SQ","title":"Swift.Equatable","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/s16SendableMetatypeP":{"title":"Swift.SendableMetatype","type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/s16SendableMetatypeP"},"https://brand.orange.com/en/brand-basics/typography":{"titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)"}],"url":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","title":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)","type":"link"}}}